# AI Memory Brain Defaults

Use this workflow by default in this repository:

1. Model posture
- Prefer local Ollama/Gemma whenever helper/model inference is needed.
- Do not switch to paid/high-tier providers unless the user explicitly opts in.

2. Storage/retrieval posture
- Treat JSONL as canonical first-write durability.
- Use Postgres MCP read tools for structured retrieval when filters/ranges are needed.
- Keep Neo4j as optional projection/relationship recall.

3. Hygiene posture
- Do not introduce cron/scheduled jobs for vault maintenance.
- Prefer explicit, on-demand hygiene commands (for example `python memory_gateway/vault_lint.py`).

4. Documentation posture
- Keep user-facing docs aligned with the above defaults.
- If behavior changes, update docs in the same task.
